Ant Colony – Privacy Policy
Last updated: November 2025

Ant Colony does not collect, store, or share any personal data from its users.
All gameplay progress and preferences are saved locally on your device and are not transmitted to any external servers.

1. Information Collection

We do not collect or request any personal information such as names, email addresses, or location data.

2. Data Storage

Your game progress and in-game settings are stored locally on your device. Deleting the app will also delete this data.

3. Third-Party Services

Ant Colony does not use analytics, ads, or third-party SDKs that track users.

4. Children’s Privacy

This game is safe for all ages and does not include harmful content or data collection mechanisms.

5. Contact

If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
